{"id": 1335, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得哪种离职方式很招人烦？", "description": "买卖不成，连情意都不在了。（题图来自：Irene Rinaldi）", "record_count": 1944, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20161116191225TAnJMVzh5BgtmbYN.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-11-24T03:00:44Z", "options": [{"id": 139532, "content": "抱怨一堆，一直说走却迟迟不走", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 855075}, {"id": 136727, "content": "一脸找到人生新目标的急迫感，带着你们这里不行的欠揍型。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 788952}, {"id": 136728, "content": "不发工资，见不到老板人，连句话都没有，公司活也没有，莫名其妙的公司人都离职了，也没打招呼。最后剩下自己蒙B了，被迫离职，还特么拖欠我工资", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 746647}, {"id": 136474, "content": "要离个职提前一两个月逢同事就通报，还都一个个让保密别让领导知道（拜托要走赶快走好吗）", "image": null, "praise_count": 94, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143082}, {"id": 136475, "content": "     说走就走，急忙投奔到下一个公司，毫无责任心。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 799350}, {"id": 136476, "content": "那种递交辞职报告之后三天打鱼两天晒网，动不动就请假三四天的那种真的恨不得弄死他！", "image": null, "praise_count": 63, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 834208}, {"id": 136477, "content": "要辞的原因就是在您这一秒都呆不下去了，还仁义?", "image": null, "praise_count": 253, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 844736}, {"id": 136478, "content": "辞职报告交上去后，领导就是不批准，最后自离。", "image": null, "praise_count": 70, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 630956}, {"id": 136481, "content": "不交接工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 113, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 225838}, {"id": 136737, "content": "下家要帮我缴纳社保的时候发现上家人事还没封存转移我的档案。做事能利索点吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1118734}, {"id": 136482, "content": "对所有人不满", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 225838}, {"id": 137506, "content": "提前跟财务预支了工资，然后第二天直接不来了，工作也没交接。关键没人知道啥原因，你丫昨天看起来还是正常的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 848650}, {"id": 136483, "content": "交接期，不工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 174, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 225838}, {"id": 136739, "content": "加班时谈感情奉献，迟到时扣钱加批评，离职时还想方设法抹黑扣屎盆子。", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1118734}, {"id": 138275, "content": "离职不需要理由", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 827609}, {"id": 136484, "content": "拉黑屏蔽所有同事", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 844755}, {"id": 136485, "content": "群发邮件抱怨", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 785595}, {"id": 136487, "content": "从来不烦", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 811474}, {"id": 136489, "content": "由于身体原因和沟通被干扰导致结果偏差，建议允许给予一次面谈沟通机会", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 844792}, {"id": 136490, "content": "自检过程，结束原因核心在于信息不对等条件下沟通者驳回面谈解释一次邀请，建议互相调整心态，优先保持双方良性发展", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 844792}, {"id": 136491, "content": "电话离职", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 444559}, {"id": 136492, "content": "离职前对业务相关同事进行说明及鞠躬道歉。俱往矣", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 844792}, {"id": 136493, "content": "大浪退去，自证裸奔", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 844792}, {"id": 136494, "content": "直接就没联系了，到后面联系上了，就说有急事，做不下去了，一句不好意思，所有责任都不管了。都不用想还交接了", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 843299}, {"id": 136495, "content": "基础申明所有个人言论仅供参考实际操作执行强烈极度在课程未毕业前实践老师根据个人能力动态平衡后续相关", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 844792}, {"id": 136496, "content": "辅助资料云战场命名及容错", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 844792}, {"id": 136497, "content": "老师自证刷招聘信息实际可备课", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 844792}, {"id": 136499, "content": "在辞职前根本无心工作。", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 788714}, {"id": 136500, "content": "怎么离职才不招人烦，嘿嘿", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 840253}, {"id": 137780, "content": "买卖不成情义在，员工想和平分手，老板不给力", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 850279}, {"id": 136501, "content": "工作有问题找不到人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 494480}, {"id": 151093, "content": "临走还拖人下水！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 524959}, {"id": 136504, "content": "消失啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 772695}, {"id": 136506, "content": "离个职让我们请他吃两顿饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 518134}, {"id": 136507, "content": "1.工作没交接\n2.大摆宴席", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 831230}, {"id": 136508, "content": "把一个很重要的文件弄没了，走了就说找不到了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 676020}, {"id": 136509, "content": "貌似这种事情轮不到小职员操心", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 261387}, {"id": 136511, "content": " 天天抱怨，天天说要走就是不走", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 844000}, {"id": 137793, "content": "我很支持大家说的各种行为", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 850483}, {"id": 136518, "content": "你得把钱还给我", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147030}, {"id": 136520, "content": "离职前还骚动其他员工，散播负能量", "image": null, "praise_count": 47, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 623421}, {"id": 137032, "content": "在另一个糟糕的地方高就", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 769693}, {"id": 148297, "content": "赞", "image": "img/option/option/20161228144944gzNQAaRsHheDBn6O.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 882913}, {"id": 136527, "content": "有些人天天吐槽，md不干了，过完年就辞。过完年了，md干不下去了，清明后就走。清明后，md真不想干了，五一后就不干了。五一后，md真受不了，干到十一。国庆后，md真心受够了，过完年坚决走...呵呵，你快点走好吗，朋友，不送...", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 774208}, {"id": 136528, "content": "工作倦怠，要辞不辞。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 609757}, {"id": 136784, "content": "交接完，之后才发现，一堆数据不见了。。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 839051}, {"id": 136787, "content": "提交辞职之后的一个月内，领导使劲叫你做事榨干你", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 615702}, {"id": 136534, "content": "世界那么大，我想去走走。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654847}, {"id": 137046, "content": "各种奇葩工作花式劝退。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 847069}, {"id": 136535, "content": "打十个电话，只会接一次！?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 803877}]}